      • SchemaValidationFilter

        @Deprecated
public SchemaValidationFilter(@Nonnull @ParameterName(name="builder")
                                          SAMLSchemaBuilder builder,
                                          @Nullable @NonnullElements @ParameterName(name="extensionSchemas")
                                          String[] extensionSchemas)
        Deprecated. 
        Constructor.

        Specifying extension schemas should be done by explicitly injecting a pre-configured SchemaBuilder using the non-deprecated constructor. Using this version results in an internally constructed SchemaBuilder using classpath-based schema resolution of any extensions or imports, with other settings left to their defaults.

        Parameters:
        builder - SAML schema source to use
        extensionSchemas - classpath-based location of metadata extension schemas
